android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATIO.description: Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

manifest_analysis.title:
Application Data can be Backed up
[android:allowBackup=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: This flag allows anyone to backup your application data via adb. It allows users who have enabled USB debugging to copy application data off of the device.

playstore_details.title: Tokenncoin – A Cryptocurrency Market Data Platform
playstore_details.description:
Tokenncoin app is an easy to use cryptocurrency market app that aims to provide the latest cryptocurrency rankings, exchange volume, crypto news and events, ICO updates, and many more.

It allows you to monitor the price changes and track the market performance of not just the top-performing cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin, Ethereum, and Tether, but also thousands of altcoins on the market.

Real-time cryptocurrency rankings

Tokenncoin displays real-time crypto market rankings. From the bitcoin price and other altcoin prices, market cap, circulating supply, and price graph, you can anticipate which crypto is most likely to gain or lose. Top gainers and losers can also be monitored. 

Monitor leading cryptocurrency exchanges

To help users in buying, selling, and trading cryptos, Tokenncoin app ranks more than 100 exchanges based on its adjusted volume and price change. Check out comprehensive details about the historic volume, active markets, trading pairs, and fee structures of Coinbase, Bittrex, OKEx, Bithumb Global, Binance, and more. 

Manage your crypto portfolio easily

Keep your crypto portfolio within our platform to monitor the performance of your digital assets. Tokenncoin app enables you to track all your cryptos and other digital asset’s value based on the live crypto market. You can see an overview of your total holdings based on the set default currency.

Follow the timeline of upcoming & ongoing ICOs

Tokenncoin app aims to provide an avenue for cryptocurrency investors to know the latest and on-going Initial Coin Offerings (ICO). Tokenncoin app will help guide ICO investors in understanding the services and offerings before they invest in the coin projects.

Latest crypto news/events

Tokenncoin app gathers the breaking crypto news from various online media publications like Cointelegraph, Coindesk, Newsbtc, and other sources. Tokenncoin app lists down conferences, celebrations, and activities you can participate in. 

Switch to Day or Night mode

Tokenncoin wanted to present cryptocurrency data in a clear and appealing window. Users are given options to view and navigate the website in day or night mode. This feature will aid in a clearer review of data to be easy on the eyes. 

Easy and convenient to compare cryptos

Tokenncoin app offers a user-friendly crypto comparison feature. Investors can compare crypto prices based on market cap and volume. The comparison data are presented within a table and shows significant information such as the rank, price, market cap, and 24H volume within 24 hours.

Currency conversion calculator

Instantly know the conversion value of a cryptocurrency to fiat or fiat to cryptocurrency using Tokenncoin’s Coin Conversion Calculator. The calculator has all registered cryptocurrencies and selected stable fiat currencies with the rates based on the reliable and real-time market. 

Crypto prices notifications

Enabling the coin alert feature, you can get notified of bullish trends or price drops in the crypto market. Tokenncoin app allows users to set thresholds and alerts by percentage or price value. The main purpose of this feature is to help investors mitigate risk and stop losses.

Why Tokenncoin?

Tokenncoin is a multi-faceted cryptocurrency platform that provides accurate information and figures that are significant components in cryptocurrency assessment. 

✅ Monitor and track cryptocurrency rankings  
✅ Check liquidity of crypto exchanges 
✅ Acquire detailed information on over 2,000 crypto assets
✅ Maximize flexible crypto tools
✅ Manage your crypto portfolio based on the real-time value 
✅ Be updated on the latest crypto news and updates
✅ Diversify your portfolio by getting information about new ICOs 
✅ Learn the basics of crypto and blockchain with Tokenncoin Glossary

The Tokenncoin app is available for free!

Download and access it now on your phone to enrich your cryptocurrency trading experience.
